SHIVAM-EMR, A Complete Healthcare Management System. 

A product for all - Desktop Browsers, iPad and other tablets, Android, BlackBerry, iPhone and other smart phones 

SHIVAM-EMR is a Healthcare Management Systems that can be used by Hospital Admistrators, providers/doctors, nurses, PCP, 
MSO, pharmacist, dispensers or whoever holds a operational or managerial pose in the Hospital, clinic, pharmacy, 
office and etc.

SHIVAM-EMR is a full-featured hospital practice management system that integrates appointment, scheduling, 
patient demographics, patient ledger, patient labs and tests, patient treatment, disgnostics, medication and discharging,
billing/collections, multimedia records, and powerful reporting. 

Scalable from a single-user office to a multi-provider/multi-location practice. 

It provide solutions which significantly increase the clinical efficiency, allowing doctors/nurses to spend more time 
with patients and less time with paperwork.


